<subSubSection id="FC8E653B876CB1361B9D50E5FDDEF89B" pageId="35" pageNumber="228" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="B42B36B0876CB1361B9D50E5FDDEF89B" blockId="35.[194,1403,285,2016]" pageId="35" pageNumber="228">
<emphasis id="86E0EAA2876CB1361B9D50E5FDBFF8E5" bold="true" box="[196,555,1783,1816]" pageId="35" pageNumber="228">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. Island populations of the Gulf Coast Kangaroo Rat may be affected by infrastructure development on the barrier islands.
</paragraph>
